clematis
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:one of the  various indigenous species of climbing plants of the genus <i>Clematis</i>, which includes those by the names of pikiarero and puawananga.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
